==Hindi==
===Etymology===
From the Old Indo-Aryan gāḍḍa- through the [[Prakrit]] gaḍḍi- (McGregor 1993). Alternatively, Platts (1884) gives the etymology as being from the Sanskrit [[गन्त्री]] ''gantrī''. 

===Noun===
'''गाड़ी''' (gāṛī)
# [[car]], [[truck]], [[bus]]
# [[carriage]]
# [[cart]]
# [[train]]
# [[rail car]]
